export function postprocess(d3) {
    console.log('I run after every render!')
    d3.selectAll('#label-axis')
        .selectAll("text")	
        .style("text-anchor", "end")
        .attr("dx", "-.8em")
        .attr("dy", "-0.3em")
        .attr("transform", "rotate(-90)")        

}
